{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><div class=\"_page_ _page_1 read-full\"><p>\n過往大台女星每逢有劇見街，為宣傳佢哋會話收視超過幾多點就以泳裝示人、報答觀眾云云。依家社交媒體咁發達，三點式照片真係day day有得look啦！有人喜歡賣弄豐滿上圍，但有時刻意而為反不及欲蓋彌彰來得誘惑。以下一班美女似乎悟出此道理，「股」惑制勝！</p>\n<div class=\"ez-toc-container\">\n<h3>\n<h2>盤點13位股惑女星目錄</h2>\n</h3>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n \n<div class=\"_more_content_\">\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_2\">\n<p>撰文、圖片：東方新地<br/>\n </p>\n<h2>1.曹思詩</h2>\n<p>因主持J2台 《Go! Yama Girl 》及 《山系女行Yama Girl 》 而受注目，有 「翻版唐詩詠」 之稱嘅曹思詩，最愛喺IG上派福利，水著火辣 「晒臀」 照任睇唔嬲。</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 曹思詩有 「翻版唐詩詠」 之稱。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/16_1183a_aunt_p4_5_21298785525f2ba4a6c46ba-800x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"800\">曹思詩有 「翻版唐詩詠」 之稱。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_3\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 今年無得去旅行，曹思詩只好不斷重貼之前的旅行照啦⋯⋯\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/choccccc_116720875_219282012727997_955112714121021907_n_16129516165fb2b70687ddf-819x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"819\">今年無得去旅行，曹思詩只好不斷重貼之前的旅行照啦⋯⋯\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_4\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 曹思詩熱愛戶外活動。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/choccccc_116931755_1019734495150979_3900485464700909347_n_292490935fb2b7095a465-820x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"820\">曹思詩熱愛戶外活動。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_5\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 火辣身材Cc Cho 曹思詩\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/choccccc_117171432_1073529693049282_8776460171536828836_n_8441943165fb2b70c06d53-820x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"820\">火辣身材Cc Cho 曹思詩\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_6\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>2.陳欣妍 </h2>\n<p>喺ViuTV 節目《美女郊遊遊》中，陳欣妍以性感山系造型亮相而大受網民關注，支持佢多啲去沙灘、泳池大解放，起碼唔使餵蚊先啦！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 網友都好期待陳欣妍的寫真⋯⋯（陳欣妍IG）\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/shirleyelephant_84089359_1852637798368847_3876869730516367517_n_16084975395fb2b847878cf-819x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"819\">網友都好期待陳欣妍的寫真⋯⋯（陳欣妍IG）\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_7\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 「因為我天生盤骨比較大，成個人嘅比例望落去就會見到一個相對又大又扁平嘅pat 🤦🏻‍♀️ 所以我一直都唔敢著d貼身或低腰長牛仔褲、緊身裙 ，真係好羨慕著得靚嘅女仔⋯⋯」\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/3_1183a_aunt_p4_5_5312704335f2ba4b2e804c-827x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"827\">「因為我天生盤骨比較大，成個人嘅比例望落去就會見到一個相對又大又扁平嘅pat 🤦🏻‍♀️ 所以我一直都唔敢著d貼身或低腰長牛仔褲、緊身裙 ，真係好羨慕著得靚嘅女仔⋯⋯」\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_8\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 成為新啤妹後的陳欣妍，人氣急升。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2_1183a_aunt_p4_5_16531624515f2ba4b0d1aca-821x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"821\">成為新啤妹後的陳欣妍，人氣急升。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_9\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 勤力做運動練股的陳欣妍⋯⋯\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/shirleyelephant_67492905_992175377797372_2741384008869522298_n_3013652315fb2b901618f4-820x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"820\">勤力做運動練股的陳欣妍⋯⋯\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_10\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>3.楊柳青 </h2>\n<p>模特兒出身嘅楊柳青，因參演TVB台慶劇《溏心風暴3》 、 《解決師》而為人所認識，身為泰拳愛好者，楊柳青慢慢轉型為動作演員，見佢練習時經常要起飛腿，難怪下盤勁fit啦！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 楊柳青同朋友到沙灘晒太陽，孖住一齊晒股﹗\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/8_1183a_aunt_p4_5_5251010465f2ba491d511d.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"993\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1000\">楊柳青同朋友到沙灘晒太陽，孖住一齊晒股﹗\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_11\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 背面線條好吸引。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wiyona_83465413_139898864186047_3697240965103318134_n_10605200735fb2ba11c6338-819x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"819\">背面線條好吸引。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_12\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 原來係瑜伽高手。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wiyona_118724871_316756036256093_8850083772785082861_n_20299115285fb2ba13e718a-883x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"883\">原來係瑜伽高手。\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_14\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 楊柳青加入邵氏兄弟成為旗下藝人轉型為動作演員，下盤勁fit！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wiyona_118671575_327287515288091_1025781613087488713_n_2308281675fb2ba167e57c-883x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"883\">楊柳青加入邵氏兄弟成為旗下藝人轉型為動作演員，下盤勁fit！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_15\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>4.林芊妤 </h2>\n<p>呢位瑜伽導師日操夜操，玲瓏浮凸線條盡現，難怪一班連登仔見親林芊妤都話想瘋狂飲 coffee 囉！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 Coffee在新年前提醒大家要為夏天作好準備，在農曆新年唔好食大個胃。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img_9256_16900315386023c541924d8-653x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"653\">Coffee在新年前提醒大家要為夏天作好準備，在農曆新年唔好食大個胃。\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_18\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 Coffee勤力操練股肌同背肌。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/coffee89921_122830370_3651254514906449_2102596940640181838_n_13225837455fb2bafe307ca-1024x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"960\">Coffee勤力操練股肌同背肌。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_19\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>5.陳婉衡 </h2>\n<p>陳婉衡曾於旅遊節目如《 3日2夜 》、《 Go!Yama Girl 》中，展現震撼上圍，擁有健身教練牌照嘅佢亦熱愛瑜伽、鋼管舞，出晒名專操「 蜜桃臀 」。</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 陳婉衡努力操出蜜桃臀。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/14_1183a_aunt_p4_5_17680114295f2ba4a0cdd1c.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"966\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1000\">陳婉衡努力操出蜜桃臀。\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_23\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>6.麥明詩 </h2>\n<p>暫別娛樂圈嘅麥明詩，酷愛潛水等水上活動，10A港姐果然識玩，偶然出吓「股」 惑，近排 「林作西裝事件」 真係太倒胃，睇番佢前度條氣即時順番晒。</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 麥明詩雖然對幕前已無心戀戰，但仍然好有戰鬥格。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_1183a_aunt_p4_5_5752640695f2ba4aeca3c6-817x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"817\">麥明詩雖然對幕前已無心戀戰，但仍然好有戰鬥格。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_24\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>7.佘詩曼 </h2>\n<p>一早上晒位嘅佘詩曼，絕對唔使靠泳裝照吸like，難得著上泳衣騷少少，呢類型相片隨時可一不可再！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 佘詩曼著住自己設計的泳衣。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/4a_1183a_aunt_p4_5_13928755355f2ba4b7c3c78-760x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"760\">佘詩曼著住自己設計的泳衣。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_25\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 佘詩曼keep得好好﹗\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/4_1183a_aunt_p4_5_637301515f2ba4b5cd958.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"940\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1000\">佘詩曼keep得好好﹗\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_26\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>8.龔嘉欣 </h2>\n<p>可能龔嘉欣都深明自己並非有「鬼影變幻球」可出賣嗰種type，佢嘅事業唔係靠事業線，艷陽下季節限定靚 「股」 照，成功draw attention！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"盤點12位股惑女星！陳婉衡「 蜜桃臀 」夠搶鏡、陳欣妍派福利唔會手軟！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5_1183a_aunt_p4_5_4983062605f2ba4b9de8a3-746x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"746\"></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_27\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>9.G.E.M.  </h2>\n<p>台上台下運動量極高嘅G.E.M.鄧紫棋，身形 fit 到漏，隨意一張坐喺泳池邊嘅大露背泳衣照，透出半股，物以稀為貴。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"盤點12位股惑女星！陳婉衡「 蜜桃臀 」夠搶鏡、陳欣妍派福利唔會手軟！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/new_1183a_aunt_p4_5_4960417555f2ba4acbeda8.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"784\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_29\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>10.連詩雅 </h2>\n<p>十五歲做模特兒嘅連詩雅，以歌手身份出道，從不刻意賣弄性感，這張不經意嘅長腿加美臀照片，一樣睇到人好似佢首歌〈血一般紅〉咁，有幻想噴鼻血呀！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 連詩雅近年愛上做gym，更操出馬甲線。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12_1183a_aunt_p4_5_14584145385f2ba49bf0b99-843x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"843\">連詩雅近年愛上做gym，更操出馬甲線。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_30\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 連詩雅身形瘦削，一雙長腿好養眼。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11_1183a_aunt_p4_5_10764333285f2ba498c842a-706x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"706\">連詩雅身形瘦削，一雙長腿好養眼。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_31\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>11.楊偲泳 </h2>\n<p>擁有32D 上圍被冠以「 巨咪陳妍希 」嘅楊偲泳，同時亦係排球聯賽球員，下盤亦非常養眼，不時喺 IG 玩水著大放送，現任男友張振朗唔會呷醋吧！</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 楊偲泳以文青女神彈起，晒泳衣照都相對密實，無三點式，但一件頭依然吸睛。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/15_1183a_aunt_p4_5_14957713065f2ba4a2e4560.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"995\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1000\">楊偲泳以文青女神彈起，晒泳衣照都相對密實，無三點式，但一件頭依然吸睛。\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_33\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>12.譚嘉儀 </h2>\n<p>巨聲幫出身嘅譚嘉儀歌藝當然有番咁上下，估唔到嬌滴滴身形都有啲睇頭，有腰有籮原來都係有料之人，失敬失敬。</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 好肉感\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/17_1183a_aunt_p4_5_5698541315f2ba4a8c80d6-783x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"783\">好肉感\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_35\">\n<p> </p>\n<h2>13. 王君馨  </h2>\n<p>王君馨去年以「G.Racie」之名自資出歌〈Casada〉兼拍MV，在《勁歌》頒獎禮上得金曲獎，成績不俗，今年再下一城推出第二首單曲〈尖叫〉，並搵來林德信任MV男主角，大玩濕身誘惑，王君馨為配合歌曲，近來打扮惹火，大玩股惑﹗</p>\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 王君馨以性感高釵歌衫出席《勁歌》頒獎禮。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img_9258_1169660526023c3d6805d8-749x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"749\">王君馨以性感高釵歌衫出席《勁歌》頒獎禮。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_36\">\n<img alt=\"股惑女星 陳婉衡 王君馨以性感內衣拍攝新歌〈尖叫〉MV，好 sexy﹗\" data-src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img_9257_12009239486023c3d87846e-750x1024.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"750\">王君馨以性感內衣拍攝新歌〈尖叫〉MV，好 sexy﹗\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"qa_box\" onclick=\"toggleFAQ(this)\">\n<p class=\"question\">將來還有什麼演唱會值得留意？</p>\n<p class=\"answer\">有不少歌手宣布舉辦演唱會，小編為你整合了香港演唱會2025一覽，包含各演唱會優先購票日期、公開售票日期、門票價錢、座位表等，想搶飛粉絲必定要留意！</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T00:35:49.142709+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1766,"images":26,"source":"WeekendHK","fallback":"none"}}